org.biohipi.image.io.RasterCodec

  • Packages that use RasterCodec 
    Package Description
    org.biohipi.image.io
    A group of classes for reading (decoding) and writing (encoding) images in various storage formats such as JPEG, PNG, NIFTI, DICOM.

    • Uses of RasterCodec in org.biohipi.image.io

      Subclasses of RasterCodec in org.biohipi.image.io 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  JpegCodec
      Extends RasterCodec and serves as both an ImageDecoder and ImageEncoder for the JPEG image storage format.
      class  PngCodec
      Extends RasterCodec and serves as both an ImageDecoder and ImageEncoder for the PNG image storage format.
